    <p>One of our members wanted to allow users to create customized information feeds in Drupal.</p>
<p>In this tutorial, we'll show you how to do that.</p>
<p>We'll show you how to allow users to choose only certain types of content to show. This could be useful for news sites, but also for many other types of site where users want personalized content.</p>
<p>In this example, we're going to create a list of movies that will only show genres that the user chooses.</p><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/ostrainingdrupal/~4/LmKH4uQDPJ0" height="1" width="1"/>
